Orit Mizrachi is a Managing Director in the GMS platform. She is based in New York.  
Since joining early in 2010, Ms. Mizrachi has been involved in various roles and most recently served as the Director of Operations for the GMS platform from 2011-2014.
Prior to joining Carlyle, Ms. Mizrachi worked in the hedge fund industry as the Chief Financial Officer of Carlyle Blue Wave Management L.P. (2007-2008) and controller at Sagamore Hill Capital Management L.P., (2000-2006), two multi-strategy hedge funds.
Ms. Mizrachi started her career at Goldstein Golub & Kessler LLP as an auditor in their financial services group.  She has a Bachelor of Science in Accounting from the State University of New York at Albany.






























