Background

		Ms. Orit Mizrachi, CPA, has been Chief Operating Officer at NF Investment Corp. since 2014. Ms. Mizrachi has been NF Investment Interim Chief Financial Officer and Treasurer since September 12, 2014. Ms. Mizrachi serves as a Managing Director at The Carlyle Group LP. She is part of Global Market Strategies and focuses on Financial Services. She served as the Chief Operating Officer at The Carlyle Group LP since 2014. Since joining Carlyle early in 2010, she has been ... involved in various roles. She served as the Director of Operations for the GMS platform from 2011 to 2014. Ms. Mizrachi served as Principal at The Carlyle Group LP. Prior to joining Carlyle, she worked in the hedge fund industry as the Chief Financial Officer at Carlyle Blue Wave Management L.P. from 2007 to 2008 and Controller at Sagamore Hill Capital Management L.P. from 2000 to 2006. Ms. Mizrachi started her career at Goldstein Golub & Kessler LLP as an Auditor in their financial services group. She is a Certified Public Accountant. Ms. Mizrachi has a Bachelor of Science in Accounting from the University at Albany.Read Full Background




